<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\user_com_interface\elasock\sam04">getsockopt</sample>
    <volume>elasock API</volume>
    <title>getsockopt</title>
    <routine_idx>ElastosSocketIndex.htm</routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>获取套接口选项。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>SOCKET</param_type>
                <param_name>s</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]已连接的套接口</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>level</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]设置套接口选项的级别: SOL_SOCKET, IPPROTO_TCP, 和IPPROTO_IP</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>optname</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]指定要获取的套接口选项</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>char *</param_type>
                <param_name>optval</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[out]指向返回所需套接口选项值的缓冲区的指针</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>int *</param_type>
                <param_name>optlen</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in，out]指向optval缓冲区大小的指针</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>当程序执行成功时，返回0；当程序执行失败时，返回SOCKET_ERROR，调用<link url="WSAGetLastError.htm">WSAGetLastError()</link>，可以获取具体的错误代码。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
    	<para>暂不支持。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <system>
            <system_name>
                Elastos 操作系统
            </system_name>
        </system>
        <headerfile>
            <file_name> winsock.h</file_name>
        </headerfile>
        <library>
            <lib_name> ElSocket.lib  </lib_name>
        </library>
    </requirements>

